    <p>Formula 1 is the highest class of international racing for open-wheel cars. Each season consists of a series of races known as Grands Prix.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>🏎️ 20 drivers, 10 teams</li>
      <li>📅 Season runs from March to December</li>
      <li>🏆 Points system decides the champion</li>
    </ul>
